snippet.title: Those who Came -Healing Solarus. Our last trailer! February 2022
snippet.description:
The major update of X-Mass of Those who Came includes a lot of new elements and show you how to start healing Solarus!
Enjoy this sneak peek into the story and the gameplay of our first co-op survival RPG for up to 4 players where teamwork is the key to save a whole planet.

Add the game to your wishlist and become part of our wonderful community!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1708570/Those_who_Came/
